r />\n這些「之」字線警告駕駛人，可能有行人正在橫過或等候橫過馬路，而且駕駛人必須讓路給在「斑馬線」上的行人。「斑馬線」所在地設有黃色燈標（通常閃動）作標記。<br />\n<br />\n你必須完全遵守《過馬路守則》。在橫過「斑馬線」前，應讓駕駛人有充分時間看見你，以便減速和停車。<span class=\"red\">如有需要，行人應首先在「斑馬線」上踏出一小步，向駛近車輛的駕駛人表示想過路。在你踏上「斑馬線」前，車輛仍不須為你停下。你須確保車輛已停定，才開始沿「斑馬線」橫過馬路。</span><br />\n<br />\n但係紅字嗰段, 無行人會咁做<br />\n你唔企出去無人知你想講馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T15:50:03.000Z","msg":"運輸署呢個建議有啲on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n架車遠, 咁直接過啦, 架車近, 仲會唔會夠彊踏前一步示意先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我記得以前學車嗰陣問師傅, 離遠見有人企喺度唔郁咁我停唔停車好?<br />\n佢問返我, 佢唔過馬路咁企喺度做咩?<br />\n講到尾都係睇司機, 駕駛態度好嘅下下都停一停啲人就唔駛驚, 呢啲永遠外國先做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026b1391a6286611f00fc3dde711a3181e841ec6","tid":2484023,"uid":172021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fccdff5058f71d9372dc4d3e4535dc6087891e10","tid":2484023,"uid":111644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46786d228e071fb6e7ce428c9bb9e6c76ad7fe5b","tid":2484023,"uid":172021,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T09:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T15:19:02.000Z","msg":"唔係規舉嚟嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T16:06:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626288be0721d58256b161f35fe796fb7cf97019","tid":2484023,"uid":172021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3898eed174c8cea952156da395a5b700d26f1072","tid":2484023,"uid":143783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46786d228e071fb6e7ce428c9bb9e6c76ad7fe5b","tid":2484023,"uid":172021,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T09:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":